  fhir:text [
     fhir:status [ fhir:v "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:div [ fhir:v "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet tiflow-xborder-operation-outcome-details-vs</b></p><a name=\"tiflow-xborder-operation-outcome-details-vs\"> </a><a name=\"hctiflow-xborder-operation-outcome-details-vs\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include all codes defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-tiflow-xborder-operation-outcome-details-cs.html\"><code>https://gematik.de/fhir/erp-eu/CodeSystem/tiflow-xborder-operation-outcome-details-cs</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?1.0.0-draft</span></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html\"><code>https://gematik.de/fhir/tiflow/core/CodeSystem/tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?1.0.0-draft</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_AUTH_ROLE_NOT_ALLOWED\">TIFLOW_AUTH_ROLE_NOT_ALLOWED</a></td><td>Access role not allowed</td><td>The authenticated actor role is not permitted to execute this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_CONSENT_REQUIRED\">TIFLOW_CONSENT_REQUIRED</a></td><td>Consent required</td><td>A valid consent is required to execute this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_ACCESS_PERMISSION_INVALID\">TIFLOW_ACCESS_PERMISSION_INVALID</a></td><td>Access permission invalid</td><td>The requested access permission is invalid or not sufficient</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_AUTH_NOT_OWNER\">TIFLOW_AUTH_NOT_OWNER</a></td><td>Authenticated actor is not owner</td><td>The authenticated actor is not the owner of the addressed task</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_ACCESSCODE_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_ACCESSCODE_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Access code mismatch</td><td>The provided access code does not match the access code assigned to the task</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_TASK_STATUS_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_TASK_STATUS_MISMATCH</a></td><td>Task status mismatch</td><td>The task is in a status that does not allow execution of this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_TASK_ID_REQUIRED\">TIFLOW_TASK_ID_REQUIRED</a></td><td>Task id required</td><td>The operation requires a task id in the request</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_KVNR_MISMATCH\">TIFLOW_KVNR_MISMATCH</a></td><td>KVNR mismatch</td><td>The KVNR in the request does not match the KVNR assigned to the task context</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_CONSENT_MISSING\">TIFLOW_CONSENT_MISSING</a></td><td>Consent missing</td><td>No required consent was found for this operation</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"file:///home/runner/work/fhir-igs-workflow/fhir-igs-workflow/igs/core/output/CodeSystem-tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs.html#tiflow-operation-outcome-details-cs-TIFLOW_ACCESS_CODE_INVALID\">TIFLOW_ACCESS_CODE_INVALID</a></td><td>Access code invalid</td><td>The provided access code is syntactically invalid</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"https://simplifier.net/resolve?scope=de.gematik.epa.medication@1.3.0&amp;canonical=https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes\"><code>https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to 1.1.1, the version found through the package references\"> version ?1.1.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://simplifier.net/resolve?scope=de.gematik.epa.medication@1.3.0&amp;canonical=https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes#operation-outcome-details-codes-SVC_VALIDATION_FAILED\">SVC_VALIDATION_FAILED</a></td><td>FHIR Profile Validation Failed</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"https://simplifier.net/resolve?scope=de.gematik.epa.medication@1.3.0&amp;canonical=https://gematik.de/fhir/ti/CodeSystem/operation-outcome-details-codes#operation-outcome-details-codes-SVC_TELEMATIKID_TEMPORARILY_BLOCKED\">SVC_TELEMATIKID_TEMPORARILY_BLOCKED</a></td><td>The specified Telematik-ID is temporarily blocked</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"^^rdf:XMLLiteral ]
